info.name: Tango 60" Dining Table
info.fcomRCopy: Step into Style. It's so rousing, you'll want to debut the Karmon collection at your next dinner party! Solidly constructed, this square hardwood table is on-trend with its crisp lines, open wood graining and compelling merlot finish. The central beveled glass insert adds an extra step of visual appeal.
